---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="School Impact | HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives">

<!-- HERO -->

<section
  class="relative h-[75vh] bg-cover bg-center"
  style="background-image:url('/images/hero/hero-school.jpg');"
>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/65"></div>

  <div
    class="relative z-10 h-full flex items-center justify-center px-8"
  >

    <div class="max-w-5xl text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-300 font-semibold mb-6"
      >

        SCHOOL IMPACT

      </p>

      <h1
        class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight"
      >

        Transforming Schools,

        <span class="text-green-300">

          Transforming Lives

        </span>

      </h1>

      <p
        class="mt-10 text-xl text-white leading-10"
      >

        Empowering students through mental wellbeing,
        public health education, Artificial Intelligence
        literacy and future-ready digital skills.

      </p>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- INTRODUCTION -->

<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div
    class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Investing in Young People

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
    >

      At HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives (HPCBI),
      we believe schools are one of the best places to
      improve mental wellbeing, encourage healthy choices
      and prepare young people for successful futures.

    </p>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
    >

      Through engaging workshops, practical demonstrations,
      interactive discussions and innovative learning
      experiences, we equip students with knowledge and
      confidence that extends beyond the classroom.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- SCHOOLS WE HAVE REACHED -->
<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">

    <div class="text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

       <div class="text-center">

  <p
    class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
  >

    PHASE ONE

  </p>

  <h2
    class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
  >

    Schools We Have Reached

  </h2>

  <p
    class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
  >

    Through our Healthy Minds, Brighter Futures programme,
    HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives (HPCBI) has
    reached students across public secondary schools in
    Lagos State with engaging sessions on mental wellbeing,
    public health, Artificial Intelligence (AI), digital
    skills and life readiness.

  </p>

</div>

  </p>

  <h2
    class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
  >

    Schools We Have Reached

  </h2>

  <p
    class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
  >

    Through our Healthy Minds, Brighter Futures programme,
    HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives (HPCBI) has
    reached students across public secondary schools in
    Lagos State with engaging sessions on mental wellbeing,
    public health, Artificial Intelligence (AI), digital
    skills and life readiness.

  </p>

    </div>

    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-20"
    >

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8">

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">

          Public Secondary Schools

        </h3>

        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-gray-700 leading-8">

          <li>✔ Mental health awareness and wellbeing education</li>

          <li>✔ Life skills and resilience development</li>

          <li>✔ Public health and healthy lifestyle promotion</li>

          <li>✔ Artificial Intelligence (AI) and digital literacy sessions</li>

        </ul>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8">

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">

          School Community Engagement

        </h3>

        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-gray-700 leading-8">

          <li>✔ Interactive student engagement programmes</li>

          <li>✔ Building resilience and emotional wellbeing</li>

          <li>✔ Promoting responsible technology use</li>

          <li>✔ Preparing students for future opportunities</li>

        </ul>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8">

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">

          Inclusive Education

        </h3>

        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-gray-700 leading-8">

          <li>✔ Inclusive school serving deaf and hard-of-hearing learners</li>

          <li>✔ Sign language-supported classroom sessions</li>

          <li>✔ Inclusive AI & mental wellbeing training</li>

        </ul>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- PROGRAMME EXPANSION -->

<section class="py-24 bg-green-50">

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">

    <p
      class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-700 font-semibold"
    >

      NEXT PHASE

    </p>

    <h2
      class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Expanding Our Reach Across Lagos State

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
    >

      Building on the success of our initial school
      engagements, approval has been received for the
      programme to continue in additional public secondary
      schools across Lagos State.

    </p>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
    >

      The next phase of implementation is scheduled to
      commence in <strong>September 2026</strong>. Through
      this expansion, HPCBI will reach even more students
      with practical learning experiences in mental
      wellbeing, public health, Artificial Intelligence,
      digital literacy and life skills.

    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-14 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-green-600 px-10 py-4 text-white font-bold shadow-xl"
    >

      September 2026 Programme Expansion

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- OUR APPROACH -->
<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">

    <div class="text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        OUR APPROACH

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        How We Create Lasting School Impact

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
      >

        We believe meaningful impact goes beyond a single
        training session. Every school engagement combines
        practical learning, student participation and
        sustainable follow-up to ensure knowledge translates
        into lasting positive change.

      </p>

    </div>

    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-20"
    >

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          🧠

        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Mental Wellbeing

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Helping students understand emotional wellbeing,
          resilience, self-awareness and healthy coping
          strategies.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          ❤️

        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Public Health

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Promoting healthy lifestyles, disease prevention,
          vaccination awareness and informed health
          decision-making.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          🤖

        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          AI & Digital Skills

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Introducing students to Artificial Intelligence,
          digital creativity and future-ready technology
          skills.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          🌱

        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Life Skills

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Building confidence, communication, leadership,
          teamwork and responsible decision-making for
          lifelong success.

        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- IMPACT DASHBOARD -->

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">

    <div class="text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-300 font-semibold"
      >

        IMPACT AT A GLANCE

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold"
      >

        Measuring Our Progress

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-slate-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
      >

        Every school engagement contributes to our mission
        of building healthier, more informed and
        future-ready communities.

      </p>

    </div>

    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 mt-20"
    >

      <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-green-300">

          9+

        </div>

        <p class="mt-5 text-lg">

          Schools Reached

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-green-300">

          Thousands

        </div>

        <p class="mt-5 text-lg">

          Students Engaged

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-green-300">

          2026

        </div>

        <p class="mt-5 text-lg">

          Expansion Phase

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-green-300">

          AI

        </div>

        <p class="mt-5 text-lg">

          Digital Skills Training

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-green-300">

          Ongoing

        </div>

        <p class="mt-5 text-lg">

          Government Collaboration

        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- PHOTO & VIDEO HIGHLIGHTS -->
<!-- PHOTO GALLERY -->

<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">

    <div class="text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        IN ACTION

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        Moments From Our School Programmes

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
      >

        Every photograph tells the story of students
        learning, participating and discovering new
        opportunities through HPCBI's programmes.

      </p>

    </div>

    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-20"
    >

      <img
        src="/images/gallery/classroom1.jpg"
        alt="Students participating"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl h-80 w-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"
      />

      <img
        src="/images/gallery/classroom2.jpg"
        alt="School programme"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl h-80 w-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"
      />

      <img
        src="/images/hero/hero-school.jpg"
        alt="School training"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl h-80 w-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"
      />

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- VOICES FROM THE CLASSROOM -->

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">

    <div class="text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        IMPACT STORIES

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        Voices From the Classroom

      </h2>

    </div>

    <div
      class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mt-20"
    >

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10">

        <p class="italic leading-9 text-gray-700">

          "The session opened my eyes to the importance of
          mental health and showed me how Artificial
          Intelligence can be used positively in my future."

        </p>

        <h4 class="mt-8 font-bold text-green-700">

          Secondary School Student

        </h4>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10">

        <p class="italic leading-9 text-gray-700">

          "Students were fully engaged throughout the
          programme. The training was practical, inspiring
          and relevant to today's world."

        </p>

        <h4 class="mt-8 font-bold text-green-700">

          School Administrator

        </h4>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10">

        <p class="italic leading-9 text-gray-700">

          "This initiative combines mental wellbeing,
          technology and life skills in a way that prepares
          students for the future."

        </p>

        <h4 class="mt-8 font-bold text-green-700">

          Education Stakeholder

        </h4>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- LOOKING AHEAD -->

<section class="py-24 bg-green-50">

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">

    <p
      class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-700 font-semibold"
    >

      LOOKING AHEAD

    </p>

    <h2
      class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      September 2026 and Beyond

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
    >

      Beginning in September 2026, HPCBI will continue
      expanding its Healthy Minds, Brighter Futures
      programme into additional public secondary schools
      across Lagos State. Working with education
      stakeholders and partners, we aim to reach more
      students with practical learning experiences that
      promote mental wellbeing, healthy living, Artificial
      Intelligence, digital literacy and leadership.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- CALL TO ACTION -->

<section
  class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-700"
>

  <div
    class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-white"
    >

      Help Us Reach More Schools

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-xl text-white leading-9"
    >

      Together, we can equip more young people with the
      knowledge, confidence and skills they need to build
      healthier lives and brighter futures.

    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6"
    >

      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="bg-white text-green-700 font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
      >

        Contact Us

      </a>

      <a
        href="/support-our-mission"
        class="bg-green-900 text-white font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-800 transition"
      >

        Support Our Mission

      </a>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

</Layout>